POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工重新登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工手动开始非本人负责项目节点，预期 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminStartNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminStartNodeId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

