### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：节点下存在子任务，不允许手动开始，预期 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{nodeWithTasksProjectId}}/nodes/{{nodeWithTasksId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：已完成节点不能直接再次开始，预期 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{completedNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{completedNodeId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminStartNodeId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：node_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminStartNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{invalidNodeId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminStartNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminStartNodeId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

[]

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}/nodes/{{repeatableAdminStartNodeId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：阶段节点不存在，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{repeatableAdminStartNodeProjectId}}/nodes/{{missingNodeId}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{}
